{"tid":2044841,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日晚餐 豬扒便當+章魚燒 & 撚廚","createTime":"2020-05-31T11:13:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T15:37:57.000Z","uid":260581,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f13494101d6a62e9d99847e26b9923fbe88e3734","tid":2044841,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:13:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9twa45C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9twa45C.jpg&h=49575a6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日洗抽油煙機 所以冇煮<br />\n晏晝出去既時候 有個法輪功既呀姨聊我傾計<br />\n原先佢都好地地 講講下佢見我係同路人<br />\n佢有d好似想我入教 同我講法輪功信佛<br />\n之後仲同我講 侵侵係因為信左神先冇人拉到佢落枱<br />\n佢仲話 早排澳洲山火 燒左幾個月都唔停<br />\n佢地一叫scott morrison信神之後 祈禱就停火了<br />\nDafuq<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28b18b9b1312321ed2b77ed3cce48b22d065197","tid":2044841,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:14:21.000Z","msg":"食咁少夠唔夠?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33258fef80d1da244a2a360865adf7fa1795f4e","tid":2044841,"uid":66409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:14:42.000Z","msg":"幾錢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f07b1ca6c9741467cd5d7e876aa916876fc08077","tid":2044841,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:14:46.000Z","msg":"很少肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca79077626b714a7ac30d3cb0daf500855d32511","tid":2044841,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:14:51.000Z","msg":"Lm<br />\n我都喺downtown遇過法輪功<br />\n佢地比我想像中正常<br />\n但熱心到有啲唔自在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6723b5a4684bd8f29caa19c1c2971f45e1935d","tid":2044841,"uid":260581,"like":1,"dislike"